data.description: The person lucky enough to buy this townhome will never regret the decision to live in paradise. Can you imagine your own three bedroom home, less than two miles from the beach with your own patio oasis in your backyard? Add to that - stainless steel appliances, newer HVAC and water heater and you have no worries. The roof was also just replaced last year. But wait, there's more! Within your community, you not only have your own pool but you are part of the unparalleled Market Common!  Offering a distinctive selection of outstanding restaurant experiences, the Market Common is in a class all its own. From renowned Chinese, Italian and American cuisines to prime steaks and award-winning handcrafted beers, your biggest dilemma will be choosing where to go first.  Shopping at the Market Common is fresh and fun with beautifully landscaped walkways, park benches, rocking chairs, bubbling fountains - even a play area for the kids. From accessories, apparel and jewelry to home décor, books, music and sporting goods, the range of offerings is impressive and irresistible.  From moving watching, billiards and bowling to escape room adventures and live music and game nights, there's plenty of family fun to be had at the Market Common.  www.themarketcommonmb.com
